Abenkwan yɛ nkwan a wɔ de abɛ ayɛ na ɛnyɛ na wa Abibiman mu. Efri  Urhobo abosuakuw a ɛwɔ Delta State, [[Alata man|Nigeria]]. Abenkwan a bɛyɛ asaasetam nkwan.

== Efa Ɔsom ==

=== Cameroon ===
Mbanga nkwan yɛ nkwan a yɛde abɛ ayɛ wɔ [[Cameroonian cuisine|Cameroonfo nduane]] ne Abibirem atɔeɛ nduane. Wɔ taa de di [[kwacoco]]. Nkwan no yɛ Cameroonfo nsiananmu ma Abibirem [[Banga (soup)|Banga (Nkwan)]], abenkwan a wo di wɔ mia beberee a Nigeria fa bi ka ho. Wɔ Cameroon, wɔ de abɛ amono na ɛyɛ mbanga. Sɛ bia wɔ wɔ no abɛ amono ni hɔ a wɔ de abɛ a ɛwɔ konkomu na ɛyɛ.

=== Nigeria ===
[[File:Eba_served_with_Fresh_fish_banga_soup_in_a_clay_pot.jpg|thumb|Eba ne enam amono banga a wɔ de adwe ayɛ wɔ kukuw mu]]
[[File:Eating_Banga_(Pam_Seed)_Rice..jpg|thumb|Ngo kɔkɔɔ moo (Banga Rice) ne nantwi nam ahoro ne nkosua ayɛ]]
Banga yɛ nkwan bi a yɛ de abɛ ayɛ wɔ anaafoɔ Niger Delta [[Alata man|Nigeria]] nkankan ne [[Itsekiri people|Itsekiri]] abusuakuw. Saa aduane no ne "Ofe Akwu"  wɔ  Igbo ammamere mu. [[Bini people|Binis]] fo wɔ nkwan bi a wɔ de abɛ ayɛ a ɛte sɛ "Ofe Akwu" sɛ ɛba neɛma a wa de yɛ ne ɔkwan a wɔ fa so yɛ.

Wɔ [[Alata man|Nigeria]], wɔ de aduane yi ka aduan ahoro bi ho te sɛ Ataredeɛ (''Usi'') ma Urhobofo wɔ Delta State, Nigeria, banku ma [[Ghana|Gana]] ne ɛmoo ma Igbo fo.

Beletete, aidan aduaba, rohojie ma banga yɛ dɛ, Banga ehwa ahaban a yɛ frɛ no Obenetietien (anaa wɔ bɛtumi de nwonwono anaa ehwa ahaban a yɛ), oburunbebe dua baako,gyeene a yɛ twetwa,crayfish a ya yam,meko ne nkyen.  Ɛda bi wɔ hɔ a wɔ de nkwan no di  mankani (taro) aduane a yɛ frɛ no ''kwacoco''. Wɔ taa de nsuomu nam amono anaa nea ya ho anaa mogya nam na ɛyɛ banga nkwan.

Nkwan no so yɛ dɛ sɛ wɔ de nkruma ka ho a.

Amiedi, a wɔ san frɛ no banga nkwan, yɛ nkwan a Urhobofo wɔ Nigeria anaafoɔ na edi. Wɔ de nsuo a wɔ nya fi adwe mu na ɛyɛ. Ɛno akyi no na wɔ de neɛma bi tɛ sɛ crayfish, mogya nam, nsuomunam, meko ne nantwi nan ka ho. Wɔ de  eba anaa usi (starch) na edi. (''Elaeis guineensis'').

